body:
Okay I’m ready to talk about the show now 😂❤️



So I ended up getting tickets for night 2 about 5 hours before the show, we were in E4! We spent most of the show by the first b stage….

And Taylor saw my sign 😭

And talked about it before dress?!?!?


Honestly doesn’t feel real still 😭



Anyway So I thought I would change my profile pic so if Taylor ever lurked me she might remember me from the show 😂


@taylorswift thankyou so so much for the best two nights of my life!

body:
Update:

So I haven’t been on here in I don’t know how long. But my life in the past month has been hectic AF! I was offered and accepted a 5 week teaching block at a small local school in a K/1 class which has kept me super busy with the lesson planning, resource making, marking etc. And while doing that I still kept up with my retail job on the weekends 😴

Then I graduated on the 22nd of June which was a super surreal day - I loved it and was super happy that my mum, Dad and nan could be there. I got to celebrate with one of my best friends and it was just an overall lovely day!

I’ve got one more week left teaching and one week today until my birthday! The big 23 - I feel like I should have my life together but I don’t really Hahahaha

So hey, I missed you guys and @taylorswift I still love you more than ever, even if I haven’t been here much lately!!
